{"type":"video_comment","id":7933,"parentType":"video","parentId":679,"uid":19469,"contents":"香港黑紫荊旗就很符合旗幟學的原則：顏色少、色彩分明、有意義、獨一無二。<br>\n<br>\n而且東亞國家的國旗多從封建時代的家紋中汲取靈感，使用單色旗幟中間加一個圓圈的風格；比如說日本、南韓的國旗。香港黑紫荊旗也繼承了這一特點。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RCJS8Md.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RCJS8Md.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RCJS8Md.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-27","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}